  <p>DCS endorsed the World Wide Web Consortium's Web Content Accessibility Guidelines version 2.0 (WCAG 2.0).</p>

  <p>This website is currently undergoing a third-party assessment to ensure WCAG 2.0 AA.</p>

  <p>As part of the operation of <strong>buy.nsw</strong> buyers and suppliers may link to documents or publications that may not adhere to the standards followed by the Department of Customer Service. If you are having trouble accessing any <strong>buy.nsw</strong> pages or content within our website, please send an email, including the link to the page you are trying to access, to us at  <a href="mailto:buy.nsw@customerservice.nsw.gov.au">buy.nsw@customerservice.nsw.gov.au</a>.</p>

